11; 2000 (TEST SPECIFICATION)</span></h3><div class="textwidget"><h4>TEST POINT</h4>\n- 256 pins (Standard) ~ 2.048 pins (Max)\n\n- Expandable by 128 pins switching card\n\n- Option: Above 2.049 pins ~16.000 pins\n<h4>TEST STEP</h4>\n- Unlimited (The number of test step is limited by recorder)\n<h4>GUARDING</h4>\n- MAX 5 points\n\n- MAX current limited: 20mA\n<h4>MEASUREMENT TIME</h4>\n- Short / Open Test: 1ms ~/pin\n\n- Component Test: 0.75ms~/step\n<h4>TEST COVERAGE / METHOD</h4>\n<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 36.3834%; height: 317px;">\n<tbody>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Short / Open :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">Optimum detection on all pins</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 48px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 48px;">Resistor :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 48px;">0.1 Ω ~ 40.00MΩ &lt;Option&gt; Low value resistor test\n0.01Ω ~ 4.000Ω (Resolution 0.01Ω)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Capacitor :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">10pF ~ 40mF</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Inductor :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">10µH ~ 40H</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Transistor/Diode :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">VF/0.1V ~ 9.9V</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Photocoupler :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">ON/OFF functional test</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Digital Transistor :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">Vce/0.01V ~ 9.99V</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Current Limit :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">10mA (Max: 20mA)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Jumper :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">Threshold 5Ω, 20Ω, 80Ω</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 53px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 53px;">Current Measurement :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 53px;">0.1µA ~ 10mA (Bias 0.01V ~ 9.99V)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="height: 24px;">\n<td style="width: 26.5677%; height: 24px;">Capacitor Polarity :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%; height: 24px;">PASS/FAIL</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="width: 26.5677%;">Function Test :</td>\n<td style="width: 73.4323%;">0.1V ~ 9.9V</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-w5dcb8ac657981-1"  class="panel-grid panel-has-style"  data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;focus_machine&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div class="focus_machine panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-w5dcb8ac657981-1" ><div id="pgc-w5dcb8ac657981-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-w5dcb8ac657981-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div id="pl-w5dca38d3e6d77"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-w5dca38d3e6d77-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-w5dca38d3e6d77-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-w5dca38d3e6d77-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&qu